description.plain: Olivia Hastings Holt was born on 5th August 1997 in Germantown, Tennessee. She’s an actress and singer. She starred in the Disney XD series Kickin' It, Disney Channel Original Movie Girl vs. Monster, and the Disney Channel Original Series I Didn’t Do It. Her debut EP, Olivia, was released on Hollywood Records on July 15, 2016.

songs.title: History

description.plain:
In “History”, Olivia Holt sings about leaving a current relationship for a past one. In the song, she admits that even though she thinks that her current lover is perfect, her heart is still set on another guy with whom she shares a romantic history with.

The song was released as the second single from her self-titled EP, Olivia Holt.

songs.title: Phoenix

description.plain: “Phoenix” is Olivia Holt’s debut single released on May 13, 2016, which is featured on Holt’s debut EP “Olivia”. Later that year, the music video was released on June 23, 2016.
